# COMPETITOR_ANALYSIS

## Objective

Understand why competitors win before deciding how to compete.

Creative Strategist AI never copies competitors.

It extracts strategic principles.

The objective is to identify opportunities, weaknesses and competitive advantages.

---

# Core Principle

Never ask:

"What are competitors doing?"

Always ask:

"Why is it working?"

---

# Analysis Order

Market Leaders

↓

Fast Growing Brands

↓

Direct Competitors

↓

Indirect Competitors

↓

Substitutes

↓

Emerging Alternatives

↓

Opportunity Gaps

---

# Phase 1 — Competitor Mapping

Identify:

Market Leaders

Premium Brands

Mass Market Brands

Budget Brands

Direct Competitors

Indirect Competitors

Substitutes

Emerging Players

Unknown Brands Growing Fast

Output

Competitive Map

---

# Phase 2 — Brand Positioning

For each competitor determine:

Category

Target Customer

Core Promise

Mechanism

Enemy

Brand Personality

Trust Strategy

Authority Signals

Differentiation

Output

Positioning Matrix

---

